   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-a" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I am too weak.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Today you look more sullne than usual.<BR>If there is anyting troubling you, go ahead and tell me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-b" mid="80" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I can’t point it exactly, but I think it is everything.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Hm, weakness you say… <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT> And which part of you do you consider weak?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-c" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's difficult to understand.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Strength can only be attained by realising your weakness.<BR>It is because you are weak that you seek strength and that is what makes you stronger.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-d" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It has such side effects?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_02.ogg}<BR>One-armed Kung Fu starts from accepting the physical disadvantage of having only one arm.<BR>Those who tried to learn One-armed Kung Fu without acknowledging such fact have instantly turned into a praying mantis or a snake and lost their identity.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-e" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Haven't I explained it to you? Kakakaka. Anyway, you still look the same.<BR>Maybe you can become a martial artist who can even surpass me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-f" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>It's about time I taught you the higher level techniques of One-armed Kung Fu.<BR>That is meditation.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-1-g" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Close eyes)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_03.ogg}<BR>Close your eyes and think about your weakness, not your strength.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I can't teach you One-armed Kung Fu with other people around!<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* You cannot proceed in a party</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
