      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Close your eyes and think about your weakness, not your strength.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>I can't teach you One-armed Kung Fu with other people around!<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>*You cannot proceed in a party</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
