   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-2-a" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Only those who have reached a certain mastery of One-armed Kung Fu can enter this room.<BR>You can do kicks and punches all you want here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-2-b" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_04.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you're the only disciple among the numerous disciples I've taught who managed to come until here. <BR>Wakakaka. I knew you'd be the successor of my One-armed Kung Fu from the moment I saw you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-2-c" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Like this?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_05.ogg}<BR>Now concentrate on your weakness and swing your fist. I'll teach you a higher level kung fu that can make up for your weaknesses.<BR>You shouldn't just follow any moves in martial arts books but tweak them to suit your own needs. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-2-open_ui_2" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Think about your kung fu.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_06.ogg}<BR>Good. Now focus on the techniques you are using.<BR>What is your weakness and what is your strength? You must find a kung fu style that suits you!<BR><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>* Select the job to Specialize into.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-3-a" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Think about the techniques.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>You still do not know what kung fu is suitable for you? Such revelations don't come easily. Don't be anxious about it.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Choose a job to Specialize into.<BR>It cannot be undone once you make the selection.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-3-c" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(…….)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="84"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_07.ogg}<BR>Me? I realized that my weakness was having no weakness!<BR>As you might already know, being too perfect can be a flaw, too. Wakakaka.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_08.ogg}<BR>Now, it's time to wake up. Remember everything you saw in this dream when you wake up!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Are you confident in your new kung fu?
Realization doesn't come quickly. Train hard and don't be impatient.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-4-a" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What were you enlightened about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Is that the weakness you were enlightened about?<BR>I'm glad that you finally have an idea of which way you should go. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-4-b" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(…….)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_07.ogg}<BR>Me? I realised that my weakness was having no weakness!<BR>As you might already know, being too perfect can be a flaw too. Wakakaka.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1907_shaolong-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1907_shaolong-4-" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A dream? What do you mean? Wait! Master!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_08.ogg}<BR>Now, it's time to wake up. Remember everything you saw in this dream when you wake up!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-a" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I snore? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Oh you woke up. I told you to meditate, not sleep.<BR>You were snoring so loudly that you made me embarrassed.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-b" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A dream? Was that a dream?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_09.ogg}<BR>Yeah, you were even talking in your sleep. Did you have an interesting dream or something?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-c" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I think I did Specialization with you in my dream.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>Tsk tsk. Meditation is a difficult skill but I didn't expect you to doze off like that.<BR>Anyway, you seem to be feeling better after a good sleep. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-d" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_10.ogg}<BR>Specialization…? I don't know what that is but are you saying that I taught you something in your dream?<BR>Then maybe you meditated correctly... </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-e" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell him about your dream.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong${sound:npc_Shaolung_4724_qu_11.ogg}<BR>I'm sure you were definitely sleeping... Well, the reason why you managed to meditate successfully must be  because of my fervour to teach you even in your dream.<BR>You should thank me for that! So, what was your enlightenment?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1848_shaolong-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1848_shaolong-4-f" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A gift?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Xiaolong$<BR>So <FONT color=#387206>{user_class}</FONT> is the path you are going to take. I'll give you a gift for finding your own path. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
